com.squareup.jnagmp

Class GmpInteger

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Number
      • java.math.BigInteger
        • com.squareup.jnagmp.GmpInteger
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<BigInteger>

    public class GmpInteger
extends BigInteger
    A BigInteger that caches a native peer LibGmp.mpz_t. This class may only contain positive values.

    Use this class when you plan to perform many operations using this value as an operand. For example, when doing repeated RSA operations, you would want to construct GmpIntegers for the modulus and exponent (which are the same each time) but not for the message, which will generally differ.

    See Also:
    Serialized Form
